divs: Sighting DetailsObject reported as a fiery meteor, straight tragectory, fragmenting, reportedto FAA office, news media and law enforcement agencies within 100 mile area. Ispoke with a commercial pilot and he confirmed the object was very highaltitude, but was a classic meteor in decay, put on spectacular light show. ThisMUFON f.I. sees no need to follow up. I file this report so that subsequentreports of ufo may not have merit. Object was most likely a meteor. K.S. 9682
